message.content:
Dear Boss,

I am writing to inform you that I will be resigning from my position at _______ Company effective immediately. After careful consideration, I have decided it is in the best interest of my career to pursue other opportunities outside of the company.


I want to thank you for all the support and guidance you have provided me during my time here. It has been a pleasure working with you and the rest of the team, and I wish you all the best in your future endeavors. 


Please feel free to contact me if there is anything else I can do to assist in the transition process.


Sincerely,

______
